================================================================
1. DATABASE CONTENTS — Open Database License (ODbL) v1.0
================================================================

The INCIDB database (the `products`, `ingredients`, `brands`, and
`product_ingredients` tables, in all CSV and Apache Parquet exports and in the
preview samples) is a derivative of the Open Beauty Facts database and is
therefore licensed under the Open Database License (ODbL) v1.0:

    https://opendatacommons.org/licenses/odbl/1-0/

You are free to share, create works from, and adapt the database — including
for commercial purposes — provided that you:

  (a) ATTRIBUTE Open Beauty Facts contributors and INCIDB;
  (b) SHARE-ALIKE — if you publicly use or distribute an adapted version of
      the database, you offer that adapted database under ODbL; and
  (c) KEEP-OPEN — you do not use technological measures that restrict others
      from obtaining the database in an ODbL-licensed form.

Product data © Open Beauty Facts contributors (https://openbeautyfacts.org),
licensed under ODbL. Regulatory and chemical fields (EU CosIng functional
categories, FDA MoCRA allergen flags, NLM DailyMed labels, and CAS registry
numbers) are factual data compiled from public government and open sources.

