3. COMMERCIAL SERVICES
================================================================

Because the database is ODbL-licensed, the data itself may be redistributed by
anyone under ODbL. INCIDB does NOT sell, and cannot grant, exclusive or
proprietary rights to the data. Paid INCIDB plans provide optional CONVENIENCE
AND SERVICES — hosted delivery, ready-to-query formats, incremental updates,
and support — and do not restrict the ODbL rights described in Section 1.
Contact: incidb@proton.me

THE DATABASE AND SAMPLES ARE PROVIDED "AS IS", WITHOUT WARRANTY OF ANY KIND,
EXPRESS OR IMPLIED.
